metadata.name: of Pelast is handsome,
metadata.description:
The beautiful and simple sorceress was soon moved by the court women and decided to marry him, but she regretted it after two years.



The whole castle rejected the sorceress, and everyone expected her to go after her eldest son, Manton, including the husband who was supposed to love her most, and who, after Hill's birth, was even more protective of her.
